#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.logseries"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:1 of
msgid "Draw samples from a logarithmic series distribution."
msgstr "从对数级数分布中抽取样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:3 of
msgid ""
"Samples are drawn from a log series distribution with specified shape "
"parameter, 0 < ``p`` < 1."
msgstr "样本从具有指定形状参数的对数级数分布中抽取，其中 0 < ``p`` < 1。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:6 of
msgid "Shape parameter for the distribution.  Must be in the range (0, 1)."
msgstr "分布的形状参数。必须在 (0, 1) 范围内。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:8 of
msgid ""
"Output shape.  If the given shape is, e.g., ``(m, n, k)``, then ``m * n *"
" k`` samples are drawn.  If size is ``None`` (default), a single value is"
" returned if ``p`` is a scalar.  Otherwise, ``np.array(p).size`` samples "
"are drawn."
msgstr ""
"输出形状。如果给定形状为 ``(m, n, k)``，则抽取 ``m * n * k`` 个样本。如果"
" size 为 ``None``（默认），当 ``p`` 为标量时返回单个值。否则抽取 ``np."
"array(p).size`` 个样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:13 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:15 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:17 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:20 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- Drawn samples from the parameterized logarithmic series "
"distribution."
msgstr "**out** -- 从参数化的对数级数分布中抽取的样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:25 of
msgid ":py:obj:`scipy.stats.logser`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:26 of
msgid ""
"probability density function, distribution or cumulative density "
"function, etc."
msgstr "概率密度函数、分布或累积密度函数等。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:29 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:30 of
msgid "The probability density for the Log Series distribution is"
msgstr "对数级数分布的概率密度为"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:32 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"P(k) = \\frac{-p^k}{k \\ln(1-p)},\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:34 of
msgid "where p = probability."
msgstr "其中 p = 概率。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:36 of
msgid ""
"The log series distribution is frequently used to represent species "
"richness and occurrence, first proposed by Fisher, Corbet, and Williams "
"in 1943 [2].  It may also be used to model the numbers of occupants seen "
"in cars [3]."
msgstr ""
"对数级数分布常用于表示物种丰富度和出现频率，最早由 Fisher、Corbet 和 "
"Williams 在 1943 年提出 [2]。它也可以用于建模汽车中观察到的乘客数量 [3]。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:42 of
msgid "引用"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:43 of
msgid ""
"Buzas, Martin A.; Culver, Stephen J.,  Understanding regional species "
"diversity through the log series distribution of occurrences: "
"BIODIVERSITY RESEARCH Diversity & Distributions, Volume 5, Number 5, "
"September 1999 , pp. 187-195(9)."
msgstr ""
"Buzas, Martin A.; Culver, Stephen J., 通过出现的对数级数分布理解区域物种"
"多样性：BIODIVERSITY RESEARCH Diversity & Distributions, 第 5 卷, 第 5 期"
", 1999 年 9 月, 第 187-195 页(9)。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:47 of
msgid ""
"Fisher, R.A,, A.S. Corbet, and C.B. Williams. 1943. The relation between "
"the number of species and the number of individuals in a random sample of"
" an animal population. Journal of Animal Ecology, 12:42-58."
msgstr ""
"Fisher, R.A., A.S. Corbet, 和 C.B. Williams. 1943. 动物种群随机样本中物种"
"数量与个体数量之间的关系。Journal of Animal Ecology, 12:42-58。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:51 of
msgid ""
"D. J. Hand, F. Daly, D. Lunn, E. Ostrowski, A Handbook of Small Data "
"Sets, CRC Press, 1994."
msgstr ""
"D. J. Hand, F. Daly, D. Lunn, E. Ostrowski, 小数据集手册, CRC Press, 1994"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:53 of
msgid ""
"Wikipedia, \"Logarithmic distribution\", "
"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithmic_distribution"
msgstr ""
"Wikipedia, \"对数分布\", http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Logarithmic_"
"distribution"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:57 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:58 of
msgid "Draw samples from the distribution:"
msgstr "从分布中抽取样本："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.logseries.logseries:67 of
msgid "#   plot against distribution"
msgstr "#   与分布进行对比绘图"

